column2: SELECT TOP # p.run, p.rerun, p.camCol, p.field, p.obj, cast (str (p.ra, #, #) as float) as ra, cast (str (p.[dec], #, #) as float) as dec, p.r, p.u, p.g, p.i, p.z, p.modelMagErr_u, p.modelMagErr_g, p.modelMagErr_r, p.modelMagErr_i, p.modelMagErr_z, cast (str (p.u - p.g, #, #) as float) as ugModelColor, cast (str (p.g - p.r, #, #) as float) as grModelColor, cast (str (p.r - p.i, #, #) as float) as riModelColor, cast (str (p.i - p.z, #, #) as float) as izModelColor, dbo.fIAUFromEq (p.ra, p.[dec]) as SDSSname FROM ..PhotoObj AS p JOIN dbo.fGetObjFromRect (#, #, #, #) AS b ON p.objID = b.objID WHERE (p.type = #)
